@startuml
actor User
participant "VoiceControlView.vue" as FE
participant "commands/voice router" as Router
participant "CommandExecutor" as Exec
participant "ASRPostCorrector" as Corrector
participant "DialectNormalizer" as Normalizer
participant "MultiCommandParser" as MultiParser
participant "CommandParser" as Parser
participant "Home Actions" as Actions
database "SQLite" as DB

User -> FE: 输入文本/浏览器识别文本/上传音频
alt 云端 ASR 音频
  FE -> Router: POST /api/voice/execute
  Router -> Router: SpeechRecognitionService.recognize()
else 文本或浏览器识别
  FE -> Router: POST /api/commands/execute
end
Router -> Exec: execute(command, context)
Exec -> DB: 读取用户偏好、设备别名、房间设备
Exec -> Corrector: correct_asr_text()
Corrector --> Exec: corrected_text, corrections
Exec -> Normalizer: normalize()
Normalizer --> Exec: normalized_text, detail
Exec -> MultiParser: parse()
MultiParser -> Parser: parse sub command(s)
Parser --> MultiParser: ParseResult
MultiParser --> Exec: 单条或批量解析结果
Exec -> Actions: 控制设备/执行场景/创建提醒/查询天气
Actions -> DB: 更新 devices/reminders/scenes 相关数据
Actions -> DB: 写入 device_status_history
Exec -> DB: 写入 command_logs
Exec --> Router: execution result
Router --> FE: success/code/message/data
FE --> User: 展示摘要；详情在日志页查看
@enduml
